<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>Letters to the editor</b></font><P>
<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">November 19, 2004 | Page 12</font><P>

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><B>OTHER LETTERS BELOW:</B><BR>
